exif=\"{}\" actualwidth=\"400\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"1\" vspace=\"1\" width=\"400\" id=\"A_252FE133547BD6683304C5\"></span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">당적밤은 일본어로는 <strong><span style=\"COLOR: #980000; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">감로자(甘露煮)</span></strong>라 하며</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">많은 일본인들이 즐겨 먹습니다.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #980000; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">공관도사의 당적밤 만들기</span></strong></span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">지금부터 시작합니다.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;</span></span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">요즘은 기계</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">로 밤을 깎기 때문에 밤으로</span></span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">과자를 만들어 먹는것도 참 수월합니다.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;</span></span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img src=\"http://m1.daumcdn.net/cfile208/R400x0/262F1E33547BD668348834\" class=\"txc-image\" style=\"FLOAT: none; CLEAR: none\" data-filename=\"밤과자20141129_095900.jpg\" exif=\"{}\" actualwidth=\"400\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"1\" vspace=\"1\" width=\"400\" id=\"A_262F1E33547BD668348834\"></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">밤은 유리알 같아서 급작스런 온도에 밤톨이 깨집니다.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">그래서 <strong><span style=\"COLOR: #980000; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">밤을 안깨지게 삶는 방법을 </span></strong>알려드</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">리겠습</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">니다.</span></span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">잘 깎은밤을</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"> 물이</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"> 잠길 정도로&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"> 붓고 가열하다가</span></span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim, 굴림, AppleGothic, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">수온, 밤의 품온이 60도가 되면 가열을 멈추고 30분간 정치해 둡니다.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img src=\"http://m1.daumcdn.net/cfile229/image/2751EB33547BD66908E218\" class=\"txc-image\" style=\"FLOAT: none; CLEAR: none\" data-filename=\"밤과자20141129_095950.jpg\" exif=\"{}\" actualwidth=\"379\" border=\"0\" hspace=\"1\" vspace=\"1\" width=\"379\" id=\"A_2751EB33547BD66908E218\"></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: